{"tid":1691332,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［太古撚入］太古城仆街保安","createTime":"2019-11-03T15:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T02:39:09.000Z","uid":154589,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6e2b37a7b0eb661e22a75de41b83c7578e678eaa","tid":1691332,"uid":154589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8QMOG1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8QMOG1.png&h=e97a8be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢條友係防暴狗衝入去商場拍哂膊頭，狗走左之後蘋果直播見到有街坊指住鬧佢幫班狗帶路。<br />\n<br />\n之後到灰衫大陸人施襲個陣佢就「捉住」灰衫，但灰色仍然可以起腳踢個已倒地既女仔。<br />\n<br />\n到灰衫發癲咬人個陣，佢就企係隔離，拉都唔試下拉開。<br />\n<br />\n有冇太古撚一齊投訴呢條仆街垃圾食屎狗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2gDEQq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2gDEQq.png&h=9b932efd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f16syaq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff16syaq.png&h=3bb9415e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dbbf68e26aa9f7a686f91cd7f17cca40c015330","tid":1691332,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:25:26.000Z","msg":"［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4711336f0103f2ade768403769b35b7c4cf9c96b","tid":1691332,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338f25fe2a1776d8ccfaa6ff1fb76cc4bf262bf4","tid":1691332,"uid":46746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:26:13.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母死保安"},{"pid":"1388ebba6eeee868ad919e1bff019506fe1cebed","tid":1691332,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15: